<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8064436>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Schemes of scutal yellow markings and other features diagnosing the morphs discussed herein. a. Morph A: Libitioides ornata (Say, 1821). b. Morph B: “clean” Libitioides sayi (Simon, 1879). c. Morph C: Libitioides sayi, striped Texan morph “depressa”. d. Morph D: Libitioides albolineata (Sørensen, 1884). e. Morph E: “yellow Libitioides albolineata”." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8064436/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

